            <thetext>See the linked Playground example. In contrast to e.g. the ui.Command demo (http://demo.qooxdoo.org/devel/demobrowser/index.html#ui~Command.html) in this sample, label and icon are set by the button constructor, not the command. But then the button doesn&#39;t show the command&#39;s tooltip (as I would expect), but rather the resource id of its icon, which is strange. Shouldn&#39;t it be possible to use a command with buttons that set their own label and icon?!</thetext>
